        Inclusion Criteria

          1. Male or female subjects at least 30 years old;

          2. Subjects with advanced Parkinson's disease who are already on LCIG (DuodopaÂ®) for at
             least 30 days;

          3. Body mass index range from 18.0 to 30.0 kg/m2

        Exclusion Criteria

          1. Subjects who are considered to be violent or subjects considered at suicidal risk by
             the investigator;

          2. Clinically significant abnormal laboratory data at baseline or any abnormal
             laboratory value that could interfere with the study assessments;

          3. Subjects with serious symptomatic cerebral disease, cerebrovascular disease, focal
             neurological lesions (previous brain surgery), any acute brain trauma requiring
             treatment with anticonvulsant therapy, or acute stroke
